docs.text: 提案された変更を含むテキスト ¶ Text can be deleted and replacement text added . This can also be combined into one a single operation. Highlighting is also possible and comments can be added inline . Formatting can also be applied to blocks by putting the opening and closing tags on separate lines and adding new lines between the tags and the content. 強調表示されたテキスト ¶ This was marked This was inserted This was deleted 下付き文字と上付き文字を含むテキスト ¶ H 2 0 A T A キーボードキー ¶ Ctrl + Alt + Del
